% Blooket - Game Basics

# Start a new game as a teacher/host
Create a quiz, select Blooket mode, customize settings, and share game code with students

# Join a live game as a student
Enter the game code on blooket.com or app, select your character, and get ready to answer questions

# Customize your avatar
Access settings in your profile to choose character skin and customize appearance before joining games

% Blooket - Study Strategies

# Improve answer speed
Practice answering questions quickly by replaying past games in practice mode to memorize common answers

# Review incorrect answers
After each game, check which questions you answered incorrectly and study those topics more carefully

# Build question sets for specific topics
Create custom quiz decks focused on weak areas to practice and improve your knowledge in problem subjects

# Study with friends
Organize group study sessions using Blooket with friends to review material together in a competitive format

% Blooket - Earning Points & Units

# Earn units efficiently
Answer questions quickly and correctly - speed and accuracy directly increase your unit rewards

# Complete daily challenges
Log in daily to complete challenge quests that provide bonus unit rewards in your account

# Participate in all questions
Never skip questions - answering every question in a game builds streaks and increases your rewards

# Use power-ups strategically
Unlock and use power-ups from the shop that boost your answer speed or accuracy for bonus points

% Blooket - Game Mode Strategies

# Blooket Classic mode tips
Focus on answering correctly first, then worry about speed - one correct answer beats multiple fast wrong answers

# Gold Quest mode strategy
Collect gold pieces by answering questions correctly - the more gold you collect, the higher your final score

# Tower Defense mode tactics
Use your rewards wisely to upgrade defenses, attack opponents carefully, and manage resources throughout the game

# Cafe mode gameplay
Serve customers efficiently by selecting correct answers - faster service time leads to better tips and higher scores

# Crypto Miners mode approach
Mine cryptocurrency by answering questions - reinvest your earnings into better mining equipment strategically

% Blooket - Account & Settings

# Enable notifications
Turn on notifications in settings to get alerts about friend activity, available challenges, and new game invites

# Connect social accounts
Link your social accounts to find and add friends quickly, making it easier to invite them to games

# Manage your profile
Update your bio, set your profile visibility settings, and keep your account secure with a strong password

# Track your statistics
Check your overall stats dashboard to monitor games played, win rate, and total units earned over time

# Join a class as a student
Accept class invitations from teachers using the class code provided to automatically join assigned games

% Blooket - Advanced Tips

# Farm units passively
Participate in public games and tournaments to earn units while competing against random players

# Master meta strategies
Learn the most effective power-up combinations and optimal answer patterns from top players on leaderboards

# Replay and analyze
Use replay feature to watch your game replays and identify mistakes in your decision-making or timing

# Create engaging quizzes
As a teacher, add images, detailed explanations, and multiple question types to make quizzes more engaging

# Host themed tournaments
Organize tournament games around specific topics or holidays to increase engagement and competition
